    public class ProjectPage
extends SettingsPageBase
    This is the main page for Project Settings. The Page has Four Panels. The AnnotationGuideLinePanel is used to update documents to a project. The ProjectDetailsPanel used for updating Project deatils such as descriptions of a project and name of the Project The ProjectTagSetsPanel is used to add TagSet and Tag details to a Project as well as updating them The ProjectUsersPanel is used to update User to a Project
    Author:
    Seid Muhie Yimam, Richard Eckart de Castilho
